<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>鼠标移入时，改变背景变色，移出时还原默认的背景色。</title>
    <style>
        .kuang1 {width:200px; height:120px; background:#000000; border:10px solid green;}
        .kuang2 {width:200px;height:120px;background:#000000;border:10px solid green;}
    </style>
    <script>
        function bian(a){
            document.getElementById("broszhu1").style.background=a;
        }
        function bian2(a){
            document.getElementById("broszhu2").style.background=a;
        }
    </script>
</head>

<body>
<div id="broszhu1" onmouseover="bian('yellow')" onmouseout="bian('#000000')" class="kuang1"></div>
<div id="broszhu2" onmouseover="bian2('red')" onmouseout="bian2('#000000')" class="kuang2"></div>
</body>
</html>
